title: Test
summary: This grouped bar chart has 3 categories of Sexual Orientation on the x axis representing 2 groups: Women, and Men.
Averaging these 2 groups, the highest category is found for Sexual Orientation Straight with a mean value of 97.75.
Followed by Lesbian / Gay with a mean value of 1.65.
The lowest category is observed at Bisexual that has a mean value of 0.65
showing a difference of 197.4% with the maximum value.
In case of Straight, Women shows more dominance than any other Sexual Orientation with a value 977.0 and it has the lowest value 9.0 in Bisexual.
